<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Endless Atlas - Explore Japan</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&family=Playfair+Display:ital@0;1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        /* --- Brand Variables --- */
        :root {
            --forest: #1E4034;
            --canopy: #2D6A4F;
            --moss: #528788;
            --paper: #F7F5F0;
            --ink: #0F0F0F;
            --graphite: #3D3D3D;
            --driftwood: #A8896A;
            
            --spacing-md: 16px;
            --spacing-xl: 40px;
            --spacing-3xl: 100px;
        }

        /* --- Base Typography & Structure --- */
        body {
            background-color: var(--paper);
            color: var(--graphite);
            font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 400;
            margin: 0;
            padding: var(--spacing-3xl) var(--spacing-md);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .editorial-header {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
        }

        h1 {
            font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
            color: var(--ink);
            font-size: 64px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-md) 0;
        }

        .pull-quote {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-style: italic;
            font-size: 24px;
            color: var(--forest);
            margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-md) 0;
        }

        p.body-text {
            font-size: 17px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: var(--graphite);
        }

        /* --- Map Container & SVG Styling --- */
        .map-container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 700px;
            position: relative;
        }

        svg {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            filter: drop-shadow(0px 10px 20px rgba(30, 64, 52, 0.1));
        }

        .landmass {
            fill: var(--forest);
            stroke: var(--paper);
            stroke-width: 1.5px;
            stroke-linejoin: round;
        }

        /* Interactive City Markers */
        .city-marker {
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .city-marker circle {
            fill: var(--moss);
            stroke: var(--paper);
            stroke-width: 2px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .city-marker:hover circle {
            fill: var(--canopy);
            r: 10; /* Expands slightly on hover */
        }

        .city-marker text {
            font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
            fill: var(--ink);
            font-size: 20px;
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(5px);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        /* Show text label on hover */
        .city-marker:hover text {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(-15px);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="editorial-header">
        <h1>Japan</h1>
        <p class="pull-quote">"Go where the map ends."</p>
        <p class="body-text">We ask questions the guidebook skips. Select a destination below to explore the trails, the quiet valleys, and the unexpected detours.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="map-container">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 500 600" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            
            <path class="landmass" d="M120,480 Q100,500 90,490 Q70,470 90,450 Q130,440 150,420 Q180,400 200,380 Q250,370 280,340 Q320,300 350,250 Q380,200 400,150 Q420,100 450,110 Q460,130 430,170 Q400,220 380,260 Q340,320 310,360 Q270,400 240,410 Q210,430 180,450 Q150,470 120,480 Z M60,530 Q40,550 30,540 Q20,510 50,490 Q70,500 60,530 Z M130,520 Q150,540 160,510 Q140,490 130,520 Z"/>
            
            <a href="/tokyo" class="city-marker">
                <circle cx="310" cy="350" r="7" />
                <text x="310" y="340" text-anchor="middle">TOKYO</text>
            </a>

            <a href="/kyoto" class="city-marker">
                <circle cx="230" cy="390" r="7" />
                <text x="230" y="380" text-anchor="middle">KYOTO</text>
            </a>

            <a href="/osaka" class="city-marker">
                <circle cx="215" cy="405" r="7" />
                <text x="215" y="395" text-anchor="middle">OSAKA</text>
            </a>
            
        </svg>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
